title: Will We Fit In At Food Network? -  Inside Eats Premiere | Ear Biscuits Ep. 332
description:
This week, it's all about Inside Eats, Rhett & Link's upcoming television show on Food Network and Discovery+! They discuss the process behind developing the TV show, the things they learned while shooting and editing the show, and how it's brought about all kinds of anxiety ahead of its release. Plus, Link AKA DJ Rhett hypes himself up for the upcoming Mythical party and Rhett tempers his back pain to finish the episode.
Be sure to check out Inside Eats With Rhett & Link on Food Network/Discovery+ premiering Sunday, April 24 at 10:30 / 9:30 CT!
